OL,4,Cconvicted of riot after national unrest
OL,6,FRiot carries a maximum sentence of 10
OL,7,Fyears and is a more serious charge
OL,8,Fthan violent disorder, which most
OL,9,Fother defendants from the recent
OL,10,Fnationwide trouble have faced.
OL,12,FThe judge told Usher: "You have
OL,13,Fpleaded guilty to a very serious
OL,14,Foffence.
OL,16,F"You will receive a lot of credit for
OL,17,Fentering a guilty plea today."
