OL,6,FFollowing the hearing, Christopher
OL,7,FAtkinson, Head of the Complex Casework
OL,8,FUnit for CPS North East, said: "It is
OL,9,Fclear from the evidence in this case
OL,10,Fthat Usher played an active role in
OL,11,Fthe mob violence that unfolded on the
OL,12,Fstreets of Sunderland.
