OL,3,CSunderland man becomes first to be
OL,4,Cconvicted of riot after national unrest
OL,6,F"He was filmed working with a group of
OL,7,Fat least twenty other people to rain
OL,8,Fmissiles onto attending police
OL,9,Fofficers. The co-ordinated and
OL,10,Funlawful violence carried out by the
OL,11,Fgroup in this incident, the severity
OL,12,Fof which forced police to temporarily
OL,13,Fretreat from the assault, made a
OL,14,Fcharge of riot wholly appropriate in
OL,15,Fthis case. The events of that evening
OL,16,Falso created immeasurable fear for
OL,17,FSunderland residents, with significant
OL,18,Fdamage caused to local businesses.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
