OL,3,CSunderland man becomes first to be
OL,4,Cconvicted of riot after national unrest
OL,6,F"We would like to praise the response
OL,7,Fof Northumbria Police, who effectively
OL,8,Ftackled the immediate situation, while
OL,9,Falso securing key evidence to help us
OL,10,Fbuild robust cases against the
OL,11,Fperpetrators of this violence.
OL,13,F"The Crown Prosecution Service will
OL,14,Fcontinue to work alongside our
OL,15,Fcriminal justice partners to ensure
OL,16,Fthat anyone threatening the
OL,17,Fcommunities we serve are swiftly
OL,18,Fbrought to justice for their actions."
OL,20,FUsher is due to be sentenced at
OL,21,FNewcastle Crown Court on 27 September.
